---
const skills = [
  { name: "SoapUI", level: 85 },
  { name: "Postman", level: 80 },
  { name: "Robot Framework", level: 75 },
  { name: "Python", level: 70 },
  { name: "SQL", level: 70 },
  { name: "Java", level: 65 },
  { name: "C++", level: 50 },
  { name: "UML", level: 60 },
];

const interests = [
  "🧗 Lezenie & ferraty",
  "🥾 Turistika",
  "🏃 Beh & fitness",
  "🎾 Tenis",
  "🚒 Hasičský šport",
  "📚 Čítanie",
];
---
<div class="section-head">
  <h2 class="section-title">Znalosti</h2>
</div>

<p class="section-note">
  🚧 Táto sekcia je momentálne vo vývoji. Obsah a technológie priebežne dopĺňam.
</p>
